very important, because this chakra
of Agnya is,

00:22:02.631 --> 00:22:08.987
it's (stuck)in place like this and it's very
difficult to open it.

00:22:08.987 --> 00:22:14.077
If you forgive everyone and forgive
yourself, then it will open up like this.

00:22:14.077 --> 00:22:17.496
