out of your palate?

00:23:16.667 --> 00:23:21.554
For some far away, some spread out,
some closeby,

00:23:21.554 --> 00:23:27.482
In this way, this power, which is
the Kundalini within you, that
has awakened.

00:23:27.482 --> 00:23:29.845
Kabir Das ji has described it
very beautifully.

00:23:29.845 --> 00:23:33.025
Now place both your hands towards
Me and look at Me.

00:23:33.291 --> 00:23:38.121
And try to become thoughtless, because
the first state is thoughtless samadhi
(awareness).

00:23:38.121 --> 00:23:42.448
Because whenever thoughts arise, they
are limited; have to go beyond them,
rise above them.

00:23:43.183 --> 00:23:46.423
Now raise both hands above your
head and tilt your head back.

00:23:46.423 --> 00:23:48.922
